  <brief_title>Add-on to Cognitive, Event-Related Potentials (ERP) and Electroencephalogram (EEG) Asymmetry in Affective Disorders</brief_title>
  <official_title>Add-on to Cognitive, ERP and EEG Asymmetry in Affective Disorders (#6559R) [Formerly #5723]</official_title>
